        // Portfolio Modals

        // Portfolio Modal 1
        #portfolioModal1.portfolio-modal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='portfolioModal1Label', aria-hidden='true')
            .modal-dialog.modal-xl(role='document')
                .modal-content
                    button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
                        span(aria-hidden='true')
                            i.fas.fa-times
                    .modal-body.text-center
                        .container
                            .row.justify-content-center
                                .col-lg-8
                                    // Portfolio Modal - Title
                                    h2.portfolio-modal-title.text-secondary.text-uppercase.mb-0#portfolioModal1Label Inn Hell 
                                    p.mb-5
                                        |  
                                    // Portfolio Modal - Image
                                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mb-5(src='assets/img/portfolio/InnHell/intro.gif', alt='')
                                    // Portfolio Modal - Text
                                    h3.mb-5
                                        | Inn Hell is a digital game, for iOS, in which the protagonist, with the help of the Devil, must smuggle beer into the skies in exchange for his spirit being free from eternal torture.
                                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mb-5(src='assets/img/portfolio/InnHell/menu.png', alt='')
                                    h3.mb-5
                                        | The game brings together two genres, roguelike and tactics and aims to evade the casual theme of mobile games, seeking more difficult mechanics and with a high learning curve.
                                    img.img-fluid.rounded.mb-5(src='assets/img/portfolio/InnHell/game.png', alt='')
                                    h3.mb-5
                                        |  I developed InnHell during my time at Apple Developer Academy. I learned a lot from making all the game structure from zero and creating my own Random Map Generator algorithm, creating procedural levels fitting the Roguelike genre.
                                    a(href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/90702563/Inn-Hell") For more info check out the game page 
                                    h3.mb-5
                                        |   
                                    button.btn.btn-primary(data-dismiss='modal')
                                        i.fas.fa-times.fa-fw
                                        | Close Window
